Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,标题：球技大会
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.52,0:01:13.79,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,球技大会开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.49,0:01:18.61,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,快接球 谁快来接接球
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.98,0:01:20.16,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,想回家睡觉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.01,0:01:27.44,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,山根同学
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.14,0:01:29.75,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,加油!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.76,0:01:30.58,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,栗原同学
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.10,0:01:33.00,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,想…想回家睡觉!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.20,0:01:38.54,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,啊～高濑!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.38,0:01:41.80,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,这么露骨的应援 一副喜欢人家的样子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.28,0:01:44.76,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,一…一组 呜哇～
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.81,0:01:48.06,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,要是往神田那边看的话 一副喜欢人家的样子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.95,0:02:02.17,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,古屋 吼～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.07,0:02:06.68,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,加油! 加油! 哥哥(ノД`)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.49,0:02:12.53,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,喂刚田 我们决胜就是和你们组了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.98,0:02:13.52,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,野吕…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.56,0:02:16.27,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,喂怎么啦 先说好我对有女朋友的家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.27,0:02:19.26,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,你手球犯规多了 下场能出场么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.00,0:02:22.68,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,出…出不了么!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.27,0:02:23.88,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,为啥!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.90,0:02:25.31,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不是 你知道规则么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.39,0:02:26.06,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,为啥!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.60,0:02:27.40,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.45,0:02:29.66,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,下场决胜局了吧 到时候给你加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.78,0:02:30.73,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,哦～谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.78,0:02:33.75,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,快点加奈也… 快和好!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.14,0:02:37.21,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,拜…拜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.42,0:02:38.33,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,混蛋千秋!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.59,0:02:40.49,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,启介
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.70,0:02:41.17,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.23,0:02:43.57,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,男生的足球 我也想参加
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.62,0:02:45.08,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那不可能的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.10,0:02:45.93,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,去也行哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.93,0:02:47.24,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,和谁换换吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.33,0:02:48.05,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.07,0:02:48.96,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,但是 和谁?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.28,0:02:50.63,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,启介 Change
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.79,0:02:54.88,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,接下来 决胜战开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.06,0:02:56.98,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,一组加油
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.21,0:02:59.13,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,高濑 刚田就由我来解决
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.28,0:03:00.73,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,好 不要手球哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.90,0:03:02.73,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,四组Fight
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.06,0:03:04.50,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那么 球门就交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.54,0:03:05.03,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.18,0:03:08.14,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.87,0:03:19.16,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,呜哇～菅原君好厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.17,0:03:20.18,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,唔 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.22,0:03:20.94,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,你看又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.17,0:03:21.92,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.95,0:03:23.15,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,你看你看你看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.23,0:03:25.37,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,小吉 你为什么要和我说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.06,0:03:29.45,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,高野是不是在看着我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.87,0:03:31.76,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不是 我又在瞎猜什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.99,0:03:33.28,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,明明影子都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.86,0:03:53.16,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,唔哇…好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.21,0:03:57.18,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,谢…谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.98,0:04:00.91,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,没…没什么 只是想接个球而已
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.38,0:04:03.67,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,你要接的是我们这边的球吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.70,0:04:06.15,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,怒 什么嘛! 好容易给你挡住了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.12,0:04:06.46,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\an8}才不要你关心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.46,0:04:07.82,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\an8}笨蛋 傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.06,0:04:08.68,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,怎么了千秋 夫妻吵架么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.84,0:04:10.64,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,啰嗦啊野吕 才不是的!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.66,0:04:12.26,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,哼 就知道唧唧我我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.32,0:04:14.11,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我对有女票的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.16,0:04:15.63,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那个球 还没出界哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.97,0:04:17.93,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,别骗我了!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.10,0:04:32.72,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,这样下去四组就要输了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.06,0:04:34.13,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,大家一起加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.28,0:04:35.14,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.62,0:04:37.09,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,一…二…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.82,0:04:40.61,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,四组 Fight
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.89,0:04:45.96,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\an8}加油×N
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.61,0:04:45.90,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,加奈肯定没给我加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.02,0:04:48.33,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,嘛 也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.81,0:04:50.81,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,都 已经分手了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.96,0:04:53.72,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,千秋!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.01,0:04:55.83,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,一副没干劲的样子干啥呢!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.85,0:04:57.47,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,快跑起来!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.05,0:05:01.31,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,什么嘛这是 真给我加油么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.91,0:05:05.74,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,给我看看你优点啊 笨蛋!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.35,0:05:10.08,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.81,0:05:19.34,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,什么啊 加奈那货
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.58,0:05:21.35,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,明明都不是我女朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.76,0:05:25.79,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那么大声喊我笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.81,0:05:27.59,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,你说这些话的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.17,0:05:31.26,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我不是不得不展现下男朋友的样子嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.72,0:05:36.42,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,冲啊 千秋!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.44,0:05:37.80,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.56,0:05:42.72,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,没门～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.15,0:05:46.11,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,早就说过了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.22,0:05:47.46,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,你这种有女票的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.51,0:05:48.81,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我是不会输的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.02,0:05:50.36,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我也才不会输啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.46,0:05:52.90,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,哈 归宅部的人怎么可能赢我运动部的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.90,0:06:00.02,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,Year
