Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.01,0:06:15.70,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,因此 大家都小心点别玩过头了哈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.94,0:06:17.71,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.94,0:06:21.18,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,小菅 暑假的时候足球队那边忙么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.60,0:06:22.83,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,还行 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.00,0:06:24.12,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,起立
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.15,0:06:26.21,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,大家打算一起去海边
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.24,0:06:27.60,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,小菅也一起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.89,0:06:30.47,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,看球队那边忙不忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.80,0:06:32.32,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,小千似乎也要来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.61,0:06:37.35,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,诶 这种事我就算了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.72,0:06:39.66,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,穿泳装什么的也挺害羞的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.18,0:06:42.50,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,诶 虽说换我也会这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.63,0:06:44.09,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,大家都会来的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.33,0:06:46.47,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,绫香和刚田还有帕特里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.99,0:06:48.85,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,就算你这么说…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.22,0:06:50.37,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,菅原也
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.28,0:06:52.89,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,拜～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.18,0:06:54.04,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,拜～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.54,0:06:59.09,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,好啦 加奈 快去和千秋重归于好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.18,0:07:00.51,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,唔 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.37,0:07:02.43,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,ch…ch…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.62,0:07:03.46,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.08,0:07:05.76,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,你们也去海边的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.84,0:07:08.02,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,啊 吖 现在还在考虑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.89,0:07:11.08,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我去的话合适么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.14,0:07:12.18,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,嗯?为啥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.78,0:07:17.32,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,好像高野也会去 我要是也去的话氛围会变得很奇怪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.94,0:07:22.94,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我很喜欢 那样的氛围
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.64,0:07:25.54,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,诶 菅原君不来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.61,0:07:27.18,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,呀 还不知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.24,0:07:28.94,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,说是得看社团活动情况
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.15,0:07:30.36,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.84,0:07:33.42,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,总之小吉和小千是确定了去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.18,0:07:44.67,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,怎么办 到了暑假就很难见到千秋了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.81,0:07:49.07,comment,,0,0,0,,注：放学后在教室留下来一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.16,0:07:48.51,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,这么做他会留下来么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.01,0:07:55.16,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,没电关机了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.51,0:07:57.16,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,一二三四
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.19,0:07:58.74,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\an8}六七八九
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.27,0:08:02.17,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,其实那天没有社团活动所以能够去海边的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.66,0:08:05.89,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,但是我明明知道自己跟高野没有希望的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.29,0:08:08.31,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,要是一起去了海边又会产生有希望的错觉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.60,0:08:11.79,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不也挺好的嘛 对方也没那意思吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.41,0:08:16.30,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,反正她对我也没什么意思 去了也只是扎心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.19,0:08:21.63,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,已读都没有显示
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.24,0:08:24.87,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,千秋真的已经回去了么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.22,0:08:28.06,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,在这里练习可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.29,0:08:32.00,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,怎么啦小菅
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.16,0:08:33.08,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,忘带东西了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.16,0:08:35.05,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,到底怎么办呢 海边
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.42,0:08:37.32,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.85,0:08:40.46,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,菅原不来真是遗憾呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.55,0:08:46.67,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,吉酱你还喜欢菅原么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.00,0:08:49.36,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,这个 我已经不…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.87,0:08:54.07,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,其实我一开始就知道没有希望的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.92,0:08:57.06,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.35,0:08:59.85,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,小千你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.84,0:09:07.88,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,千秋 他是不是已经不打算跟我重归于好了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.51,0:09:12.52,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,真的回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.24,0:09:15.64,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,今年的暑假要独自一人了么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.89,0:09:21.59,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,抱歉了 问你奇怪的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.72,0:09:23.69,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我去趟厕所
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.88,0:09:25.25,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.45,0:09:32.46,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,确实最近总是全想着菅原君的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.27,0:09:39.78,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,海边也是 要是菅原君不来的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.32,0:09:46.26,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,啊嘞 怎么了吉…酱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.73,0:09:53.72,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,这么慢呢 干什么去了么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.97,0:09:57.24,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,给你发短信了你没看到么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.03,0:10:00.00,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,抱歉 电池没电了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.13,0:10:02.34,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,有话想跟你就在这等着了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.71,0:10:05.36,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,怎么 你打算跟我和好么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.04,0:10:10.28,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不 我们已经分手了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.14,0:10:14.33,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,怎…怎么了菅原君
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.88,0:10:16.64,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,啊 忘带钱包
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.23,0:10:20.16,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,高野呢 一个人练习?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.34,0:10:23.31,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,没 吉酱刚去厕所了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.72,0:10:24.54,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.88,0:10:28.38,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.42,0:10:30.58,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,菅原君你不去海边吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.96,0:10:36.14,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,怎么说呢 一开始我以为不管怎么样至少也不会分手的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.40,0:10:37.86,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,说实话是我轻视了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.93,0:10:42.34,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,要是就这样和好 那件事就当没发生一样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.61,0:10:43.44,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,感觉很糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.56,0:10:47.46,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我觉得这样的交往方式不会很长久
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.11,0:10:49.19,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,好好分手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.70,0:10:54.76,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,在那之后请允许我 再一次表白吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.11,0:11:03.43,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,唔嗯 我决定不去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.46,0:11:04.79,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,为什么 社团活动?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.16,0:11:09.07,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不是 那个 我不是很擅长应付这些的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.88,0:11:11.14,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,高野你会去的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.32,0:11:12.40,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,玩的开心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.72,0:11:15.32,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,没有菅原的话我觉得我不会开心的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.89,0:11:23.23,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那你试着表白看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.92,0:11:25.47,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我会拒绝一百次的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.74,0:11:27.17,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.42,0:11:29.06,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,要用心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.76,0:11:30.47,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.96,0:11:34.01,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我不想再失去加奈了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.06,0:11:40.08,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,请和我 请和我交往吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.07,0:11:48.87,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.78,0:11:51.81,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,真难办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.42,0:11:57.14,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那 去海边用的泳衣 得去买呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.01,0:12:03.13,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.05,0:12:23.28,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,夏天 开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,
