Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.26,0:00:24.69,children opjp,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}ほらね今も君のこと考えちゃうの
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.65,0:00:32.50,children opjp,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}好きと嫌い交互に数えてゆく占い
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.72,0:00:36.36,children opjp,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}2分の (1の) 確率 (それじゃ)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.42,0:00:40.44,children opjp,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}踏み出せないね
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.27,0:00:48.74,children opjp,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}きっと あぁ この関係は曖昧模糊っていうのかな
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.90,0:00:54.18,children opjp,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}徒然でも I wish I feel my sweet
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.37,0:00:58.29,children opjp,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}大事にしなくちゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.98,0:00:17.90,children opch,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}微不足道的事情也会觉得很特别
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.26,0:00:24.69,children opch,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}此时此刻也在想念着你的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.65,0:00:32.50,children opch,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}喜欢与讨厌相互交替的占卜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.72,0:00:36.36,children opch,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}一半一半的概率的话
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.42,0:00:40.44,children opch,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}还是跨不出这一步
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.27,0:00:48.74,children opch,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}我们的关系可以说是暧昧模糊吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.90,0:00:54.18,children opch,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}虽然无聊但还是希望能感受到属于我的甜蜜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.37,0:00:58.29,children opch,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}要珍视这份感情
