Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.30,0:11:05.52,children edjp,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}あの頃と同じ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.56,0:11:09.10,children edjp,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}熱を感じてる
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.60,0:11:13.57,children edjp,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}君といつだって
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.61,0:11:18.86,children edjp,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}同じ思い出ばかり
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.20,0:11:23.95,children edjp,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}薄れてしまう
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.12,0:11:27.12,children edjp,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}君の面影を
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.20,0:11:31.62,children edjp,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}見失うのが  怖くて
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.83,0:11:34.46,children edjp,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}たった一瞬の
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.59,0:11:36.92,children edjp,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}その景色を
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.01,0:11:43.30,children edjp,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}閉じ込めたくて  だけど
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.43,0:11:48.73,children edjp,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}あなたに出会えたことで
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.02,0:11:55.27,children edjp,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}強くいられたんだ ずっと
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.32,0:12:00.45,children edjp,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}明日も目が覚めたとき
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.82,0:12:06.33,children edjp,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}すぐ隣にいる  と思ってた
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.41,0:12:12.42,children edjp,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}ただそれだけでいいのに
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.97,0:11:02.26,children edch,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}回首仰望过去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.30,0:11:05.52,children edch,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}依然同那时一样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.56,0:11:09.10,children edch,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}感受着你的热量
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.60,0:11:13.57,children edch,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}无论何时同你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.61,0:11:18.86,children edch,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}全都是同样的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.20,0:11:23.95,children edch,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}逐渐淡薄了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.12,0:11:27.12,children edch,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}你的面庞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.20,0:11:31.62,children edch,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}害怕这逐渐的  忘记
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.83,0:11:34.46,children edch,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}只是一瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.59,0:11:36.92,children edch,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}想把这份风景
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.01,0:11:43.30,children edch,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}锁进我的心里  但是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.43,0:11:48.73,children edch,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}想与你相见这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.02,0:11:55.27,children edch,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}却很需要勇气  一直如此
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.32,0:12:00.45,children edch,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}明明只是希望
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.82,0:12:06.33,children edch,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}明天当我  睁开眼的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.41,0:12:12.42,children edch,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fad(150,150)}你能在我身旁而已
